    },
    en: {
      back: 'Back to Home',
      title: 'Privacy Policy',
      updated: 'Last updated: April 2026',
      h1: '1. Overview',
      p1: 'AIbubu (hereinafter "the App") is a desktop pet application that visualizes your AI coding tool usage. We take user privacy seriously, and this policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.',
      h2: '2. Information Collection',
      p2a: 'The App runs entirely on your local machine. <strong>No personal data is sent to any remote server.</strong> Specifically:',
      p2b: '<strong>Activity data</strong>: The App detects local processes to determine the usage status of AI development tools (e.g. Cursor, Claude Code). This data is stored only on your device and is never uploaded.',
      p2c: '<strong>Steps and history</strong>: Daily step counts, active duration, and other statistics are saved in local storage only.',
      p2d: '<strong>User settings</strong>: Nickname, theme preference, selected character, and other configurations are saved locally.',
      p2e: '<strong>LAN social</strong>: When LAN features are enabled, your nickname, step count, and character info are broadcast within the local network to other users. This data never leaves your LAN.',
